    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 requirements matrix. CFD-predicted hemolysis index values show NRMSE of 12.4% against experimental data, with all 5 COU operating points yielding RH < 1 against the predicate device. The credibility evidence package, including the hemolysis constitutive model methodology reviewed in the literature, supports the conclusion that the CFD model is fit for the stated COU. The submission is accepted for 510(k) regulatory support.",
